# ── Gemini Web Authentication ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Get these from https://gemini.google.com (logged in)
# DevTools (F12) → Application → Cookies → Copy values
#
# Required:
GEMINI_PSID="your-__Secure-1PSID-cookie-here"
GEMINI_PSIDTS="your-__Secure-1PSIDTS-cookie-here"

# Optional:
GEMINI_PROXY="http://127.0.0.1:7890"

